Class Elevator

  • java.lang.Object
    • cwThree.Elevator

  • public class Elevator
extends java.lang.Object
    This class creates an elevator with the methods to visit the building floor by floor picking and alighting customers. Constructor defaults NUM_OF_FLOORS = 0, currentFloor = 0;

    1.0
    Author:
